<h2 id="the-cat-api">The cat API</h2>

<p>List cat methods</p>

<div class="language-r highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">cat_</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="c1">#&gt; =^.^=</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="c1">#&gt; /_cat/allocation</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="c1">#&gt; /_cat/shards</span><span class="w">
